{"tid":1535560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地鐵真係好撚驚人跳閘","createTime":"2019-09-03T11:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T12:57:05.000Z","uid":40672,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2bc5e6d01b67c22fddab5cd8850c3f09645dceda","tid":1535560,"uid":40672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:44:24.000Z","msg":"1930 九龍塘個個閘機都有黃衫查飛狗望住"},{"pid":"1fa62adb50f8adf1d75632b1b2e03e2a27014fd3","tid":1535560,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:45:00.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？我們需要更多！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530124</a>"},{"pid":"9d5ed786608a814fe43dbb88a69fc7c47cad16a2","tid":1535560,"uid":143699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:47:41.000Z","msg":"大家真係冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上太子站黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映錯誤示範</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBkjO1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBkjO1B.gif&h=c106dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位狗狗好明顯冇睇教學片啦，大家千奇唔好學佢啊，動作要標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n-最近黨鐵多咗狗，如果情況唔允許，希望大家都唔好勉強，可以改用老人卡。唔好因為咁而被人捉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完整示範片段：\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=217032a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"c5ac852983895f8f7bde6224f97395c84ba07479","tid":1535560,"uid":147916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:51:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GrVwe6J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGrVwe6J.jpg&h=7d8530f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幫你補圖"},{"pid":"3fda336a6c528713a552ca166fc9f22140518e25","tid":1535560,"uid":177736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"岩岩葵芳有位巴打 你好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係唔敢跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e6a90807da8be958572d9d1360433a84530548","tid":1535560,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:05:19.000Z","msg":"年輕人身手好，中女姐姐表示跳唔起呀"},{"pid":"e584848284340f3ad2e470bf380e25b5d5f5360c","tid":1535560,"uid":69416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:09:20.000Z","msg":"沙田有都唔敢捉<br />\n最多會講句「你唔可以咁樣架喎」<